%90%C3%A0o/poem-QkQttHIhfxs7qPiGEzdkiA">Ký tặng Tiết Đào - 寄贈薛濤</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Ch%E1%BA%A9n/author-bMSP5YOXWyK1jTzTI9MKNQ">Nguyên Chẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/M%E1%BA%A1n-th%C3%A0nh-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BB%A7-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-UiOxFIUmBXmMzrvmsvg2eg">Mạn thành nhị thủ kỳ 1 - 漫成二首其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Th%C3%BAc-Tr%E1%BB%B1c/Tr%C3%B9ng-ng%E1%BB%8D-nh%E1%BA%ADt-ph%E1%BA%A7n-ho%C3%A1-vong-th%C3%AA-c%C3%A2n-l%E1%BA%A1p-y-ph%E1%BB%A5c-t%E1%BA%A1i-m%E1%BB%99-c%E1%BA%A3m-t%C3%A1c/poem-RKbYHfnWSmPLFq5jsoPgSw">Trùng ngọ nhật phần hoá vong thê cân lạp y phục tại mộ cảm tác - 重午日棼化亡妻巾笠衣服在墓感作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Th%C3%BAc-Tr%E1%BB%B1c/author-0CTnEDQGEKViETWZXrhgww">Phan Thúc Trực</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BA%A3o-H%E1%BA%A3o-thi/poem-ZLgiAlRmZdlWf7MkDKd1sg">Trương Hảo Hảo thi - 張好好詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/author-3vzgm_fq7JLuFBSuENsFJw">Đỗ Mục</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-T%C3%ADch-K%E1%BB%B3/V%C5%A9-trung-qu%C3%A1-Th%E1%BA%A5t-L%C3%BD-lung-ca/poem-t1zljGkZZw_rj7vXYCTTVw">Vũ trung quá Thất Lý lung ca - 雨中過七里瀧歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-T%C3%ADch-K%E1%BB%B3/author-leXS2a46kBYHa9AoDh5zfw">Ngô Tích Kỳ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
